      "scene": "ClaudeComposerAsk",
      "narration_text": "The four dimensions of specificity are what I want to drill into with my own weak prompts. Take my request 'write a summary': (1) rewrite it specifying length, format, audience, and required components the way your three-sentence plain-language example does, (2) show me how each dimension I leave blank becomes a degree of freedom Claude fills with a default, and (3) apply the 'capable new employee with no context' test to catch what I assumed but never stated.",
